== 与布什家族的关系 ==
麦格劳家族与[[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]家庭的关系可以追溯到好几代人。已故的{{Link-en|小哈罗德·麦格劳|Harold McGraw Jr.}}就曾经是{{Link-en|芭芭拉·布什家庭扫盲基金会|Barbara Bush Foundation for Family Literacy}}的全国筹款顾问和基金董事会的创始成员。<ref name="Bushes">{{cite web|last1=Metcalf|first1=Steven|title=Reading Between the Lines|url=https://www.thenation.com/article/reading-between-lines/|website=The Nation|accessdate=2017-06-09|date=2002-01-10|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603011354/https://www.thenation.com/article/reading-between-lines/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

